[[File:Comoran Defense Force.jpg|thumb|right|Comoran Defense Force soldiers march in formation in [[Moroni, Comoros|Moroni]]]]
[[File:Hand-to-hand combat skills of the Comoran Army.jpg|thumb|right|Comoran Defense Force soldiers demonstrate hand-to-hand combat skills]]
The '''[[Comoros|Comorian]] Security Force''' (French ''Armée nationale de développement'') consist of a small standing army and a 500-member police force, as well as a 500-member defense force. A defense treaty with France provides naval resources for protection of territorial waters, training of Comorian military personnel, and air surveillance. [[France]] maintains a small troop presence in Comoros at government request. France maintains a small maritime base and a [[French Foreign Legion|Foreign Legion]] Detachment (DLEM) on [[Mayotte]].

== Equipment inventory ==
* [[FN FAL]] Assault Rifle
* [[AK-47]] Assault Rifle
* [[NSV (machine gun)|NSV]] HMG
